last_movies.title: 查斯基、父亲和橄榄林保卫战

introduction: Adam Gutniak is a Swedish actor based in Stockholm. He had main roles in the feature film Tsatsiki – farsan och olivkriget (2015), 2 years theater in SUNE, on stage with Pernilla Wahlgren, Morgan Alsing, Måns Nathanaelsson, Göran Gillinger, Hanna Hedlund, and Amy Deasismont.  Adam was starring in SVT series DRÖM with Lion Monn among others.
